title: An error occurred while creating a new notebook.
body_html:
I following Caffe2 Tutorials Overview

When I run ./start_ipython_notebook.sh ，Jupyter interface pops up.
I am trying to create a new python file，Error message appears as follows.

An error occurred while creating a new notebook.
Unexpected error while running post hook save: [Errno 2] No such file or directory.

But I run jupyter notebook in other directories without this problem.

body:
I following [Caffe2 Tutorials Overview](https://caffe2.ai/docs/tutorials.html#null__new-to-deep-learning)

When I  run` ./start_ipython_notebook.sh` ，Jupyter interface pops up.
I am trying to create a new python file，Error message appears as follows.
```
An error occurred while creating a new notebook.
Unexpected error while running post hook save: [Errno 2] No such file or directory.
```
But I run `jupyter notebook` in other directories without this problem.
